Zardus nods. "Good. Exactly what capabilities does this Hellgate have?"

His comm recieves the transmission from the Infecticons, and he looks at Wolfgang.

"I just recieved a transmission I must take care of, Wolfgang. Can you finish up with Daemos?"

As he says that, his comm replies to Composer: "Good job. Can you go report that to Wheeljack, and give him any help he might need?"
